room_title: Escape room "When Worlds Collide" by 3rd Day Escape in San Diego
room_address: 7969 Engineer Rd. Suite 215 San Diego, CA 92111
room_description:
Trapped in the Fantasy Realm, you find yourselves in the abode of a powerful wizard. You must crack his puzzles and spells to find the hidden crystal and bring it back to receive your payday.
If you happen to be in the Reality Realm, your mission is to discover the secrets of the villain's' study in order to find the crystal and save your world!
